\& CAG      169/s   \-\-  \-21% \-24%  \-32% \-32%     \-34%   \-59%     \-63%   \-67%    \-67% \-67%   \-67%
\& moOse    215/s  27%    \-\-  \-3%  \-13% \-13%     \-15%   \-48%     \-53%   \-58%    \-58% \-58%   \-58%
